SETUP
Creating Hugging Face Access Token
To create a hugging face access token, go to the hugging face website and login to your account. After that, go to Settings > Access Tokens and click on "Create new token".

  1. Go to the Hugging Face website and log in to your account.
  2. Navigate to Settings > Access Tokens.
  3. Click on "Create new token."
  4. Change the token type to "Read" and create the token.
  5. Copy the generated API key for future use.
  6. Model Selection: Choose model in that
  7. And use in code


DEPENDENCIES
pip install -r requirements.txt


TO RUN THE APPLICATION
streamlit run .\app.py
